## Common Issues & Solutions

### "Database connection error"
- Check MySQL is running
- Verify database name and credentials in `config/database.php`
- Make sure database was imported successfully

### "QR Code not generating"
- Install phpqrcode library
- Check write permissions on uploads/qr_codes/
- Verify GD extension is enabled in PHP

### "Page not found" or "404 Error"
- Check SITE_URL in config.php matches your actual URL
- Verify .htaccess file exists (for Apache)
- Make sure mod_rewrite is enabled

### Images not uploading
- Check write permissions on upload folders (777)
- Verify upload_max_filesize in php.ini (at least 10M)
- Check post_max_size in php.ini

